This paper deals with user authentication and security, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of Bluetooth Low Energy beacons for location awareness and the expressiveness of Attribute-Based Encryption suggests that this paper may also fall under the sub-categories of systems and information theory (cs.SI), cryptography and security (cs.CY), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and software engineering (cs.SE).
